text: puok del kmean chomnue nei aah li ki tab ning puok mou sh ri kin min penh chetd aoy mcheasa robsa puok anak banhchouh brakear la namuoy dl puok anak laey . haey a l laoh mean setthi kamnt kdei me tda krounea robsa trong towleu bokkol na mneak del trong mean chetnea . haey a l laoh meankar braosa bratan da thomtheng
